script.name: !move.buildcomplex
script.sourceplaintext:
* ============================================== * Build a Complex * ============================================== * Automatically builds a complx from a list of stations * Uses HephCorp do get the placement positions * The script will send the ship to the shipyard to buy each station * ============================================== * Author: Cycrow * Date: 2020/07/18 * ==============================================
$page.id = 6020 $DEFINE.OOSMOVE = [TRUE]
skip if $a.owner $a.owner = [TRUEOWNER]
if [TRUEOWNER] != Player do if [THIS] -> is hired $a.owner = Player end
* set up the command texts, so the player knows whats going on $text = read text: page=$page.id id=283 [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$text
@ = wait 100 ms
$stored.extensions = 0
* if we are to restrore a previous attempt, check the stored data if $a.restore $store.data = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='build.complex' if $store.data $a.sectorPos = $store.data[0] $a.complex = $store.data[1] $table.stations = $store.data[2] $table.shipyards = $store.data[3] $stations.array = $store.data[4] $position.array = $store.data[5] $mines.not.moved = $store.data[6] $table.built = $store.data[7] $total.stations = $store.data[8] $complex.hub = $store.data[9] $complex.tubes = $store.data[10] $table.existing = $store.data[11] $table.remove = $store.data[12] $stored.extensions = $store.data[13] @ = wait 100 ms end end
$complex.sector = $a.sectorPos[3]
* not stored data to restore, so we start the process from the beginning if not $store.data $a.complex = clone table $a.complex
@ = wait 1000 ms $table.remove = table alloc
* combine stations and mine tables $table = $a.complex['stations'] if $table $table.stations = clone table $table else $table.stations = table alloc end
$table = $a.complex['asteroids'] if $table $key = get next key: table=$table key=null while $key $station.type = $table[$key] gosub sub.AddStation $key = get next key: table=$table key=$key end end
$table.existing = table alloc $table = $a.complex['existing'] if $table $key = get next key: table=$table key=null while $key if $key -> exists if $key -> is of class Complex Hub $complex.hub = $key -> get ware type code of object $complex = $key ->get factories connected to complex $table.existing[$key] = $complex.hub if $complex $i = size of array $complex while $i dec $i = $station = $complex[$i] $station.type = $station -> get ware type code of object gosub sub.AddStation end end else $station.type = $key -> get ware type code of object $table.existing[$key] = $station.type gosub sub.AddStation end end $key = get next key: table=$table key=$key end end
@ = wait 1000 ms
* get positions of station @ $array.kits = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getkits : Include HQ=$a.includeHQ Closest=[THIS] skip if $complex.hub $complex.hub = $array.kits[0] $complex.tubes = $array.kits[2]
@ = wait 1000 ms
@ $ret = [THIS] -> call script plugin.X2I.HephCorp.getpositions : Complex Hub=$complex.hub Table of stations=$table.stations position array=$a.sectorPos No Waits=[FALSE]
$stations.array = $ret[0] $position.array = $ret[1]
@ = wait 1000 ms
* find shipyards for all stationos $table.shipyards = table alloc $i = size of array $stations.array while $i dec $i = $station.type = $stations.array[$i] if not $table.shipyards[$station.type] if [TRUEOWNER] == Player @ $shipyard = [THIS] -> call script lib.player.bestshipyard.station : Station Type=$station.type Closest Object=[THIS] Only Known=[TRUE] else @ $shipyard = [THIS] -> call script !lib.get.race.station : Race=[TRUEOWNER] Type=$station.type Closest To=[THIS] Only Known=[FALSE] Class/Type=Shipyard end do if $shipyard -> exists $table.shipyards[$station.type] = $shipyard @ = wait 10 ms end end
@ = wait 1000 ms
* setup data storage $mines.not.moved = table alloc $table.built = table alloc $total.stations = size of array $stations.array
* Store the initial setup, this is the point the command can be stopped and resume gosub sub.StoreData end
$table.blacklist = table alloc
* Loop until all stations are built, the stations are removed from array when buil while size of array $stations.array @ = wait 1000 ms
if $table.existing if size of table $table.existing gosub sub.MoveExisting continue end end
* check if we need to move any mines * if the player was in sector at construction, we dont move it initially * once they leave, we can safetly adjust the positions if not [THIS] -> is in active sector $key = get next key: table=$mines.not.moved key=null while $key $station = $key $key = get next key: table=$mines.not.moved key=$key
$positions = $mines.not.moved[$station] $x = $positions[0] $y = $positions[1] $z = $positions[2] $station ->force position: x=$x y=$y z=$z remove key $station from table $mines.not.moved end end
* check if we have any stations already in cargo hold $table.bought = table alloc $i = size of array $stations.array while $i dec $i = $station.type = $stations.array[$i] if not $table.bought[$station.type] $amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $station.type in cargo bay do if $amt $table.bought[$station.type] = $amt end end
* table.bought contains a lst of stations in cargo hold, ie just been bought if not size of table $table.bought
@ = wait 1000 ms
* find the next station type to attempt to buy gosub sub.GetStation if not $station.type gosub sub.Idle continue end
$remaining = size of array $stations.array $done.count = $total.stations - $remaining + 1 $done.count = convert number $done.count to string $text = convert number $total.stations to string $remaining.text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=284, $done.count, $text, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$remaining.text
@ = wait 1000 ms
[THIS] ->set destination to $shipyard
$sector = $shipyard -> get sector gosub sub.Resupply @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$shipyard if $ret == FLRET_NOPATH $time = playing time $time = $time + 600 $table.blacklist[$sector] = $time gosub sub.Idle continue end
@ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetostation : station=$shipyard @ = wait 1000 ms
if [DOCKEDAT] == $shipyard [THIS] ->set destination to null @ = wait 3000 ms gosub sub.BuyStations end
[THIS] ->set destination to null
@ = wait 1000 ms end
* check for any stations on board if size of table $table.bought * if we have the complex hub, we need to buy the tubes if $table.bought[$complex.hub] gosub sub.SearchTubes do if $ret.continue continue end
gosub sub.MoveToBuildStation
@ = wait randomly from 10000 to 20000 ms
$station.type = get next key: table=$table.bought key=null while $station.type $amt = $table.bought[$station.type]
while $amt dec $amt = gosub sub.BuiltStation @ = wait randomly from 5000 to 10000 ms end
$station.type = get next key: table=$table.bought key=$station.type end
@ = wait 1000 ms end end
* store final set of data while we wait gosub sub.StoreData
* check if we still need tubes gosub sub.NeededTubes while $tubes > 0 @ = wait 1000 ms gosub sub.SearchTubes do if $ret.continue gosub sub.Idle @ = wait 1000 ms gosub sub.NeededTubes end
* store final set of data while we wait gosub sub.StoreData
* make sur we are at our home sector gosub sub.MoveHome
* inform the player they need to enter the sector to finish construction if not [THIS] -> is in active sector $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=290, null, null, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$text
$text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=291, [THIS], $complex.sector, null, null, null send incoming message $text to player: type:[Log.Normal], display it=[FALSE]
while not [THIS] -> is in active sector @ = wait 2000 ms end end
@ = wait 5000 ms
* find the complex hub in the build stations list $complex.hub = null $key = get next key: table=$table.built key=null while $key if $key -> is of class Complex Hub $complex.hub = $key break end $key = get next key: table=$table.built key=$key end
* check we have enough tubes if $complex.hub -> exists $complex.type = $complex.hub -> get ware type code of object $complex.type = get construction kit from complex type: $complex.type $tubes = get complex connection tubes count: stationtype=$complex.type $stations.built = size of table $table.built $stations.built = $stations.built - $tubes - 1 $got.tubes = 0 if $complex.tubes $got.tubes = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $complex.tubes in cargo bay do if $stored.extensions > 0 $got.tubes = $got.tubes + $stored.extensions end $stations.built = $stations.built - $got.tubes
* not enough tubes, we need to remove some of the stations from the link while $stations.built > 0 $station = get random key: table=$table.built if $station != $complex.hub remove key $station from table $table.built dec $stations.built = end end * now remove the tubes from the cargo hold if $got.tubes $got.tubes = - $got.tubes = [THIS] -> add $got.tubes units of $complex.tubes end
* finally do the actual connection, and display a cutscene $complex.hub ->disconnect complex = $complex.hub ->connect complex (in active sector): factories=$table.built @ START [NULL] -> call script !lib.play.cutscene : Station=$complex.hub TL=[THIS] Delay=500
if $table.remove $obj = get next key: table=$table.remove key=null while $obj if $obj -> exists $money = $obj -> get money if $money $complex.money = $complex.hub -> get money $complex.money = 2000000000 - $complex.money if $money > $complex.money $money = $money - $complex.money $complex.hub ->add money: $money add money to player: $money else $complex.hub ->add money: $money end end $tWares = $obj ->get station tradeable ware table if $wares $ware = get next key: table=$tWares key=null while $ware $amt = $obj -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay = $complex.hub -> add $amt units of $ware $ware = get next key: table=$tWares key=$ware end end $obj ->destruct: show no explosion=[TRUE] end $obj = get next key: table=$table.remove key=$obj end end end
* clear saved data now we have finished [THIS] ->set local variable: name='build.complex' value=null if [TRUEOWNER] != Player if [THIS] -> is hired [THIS] ->set hired: [FALSE] end end * ======================================= return null * =======================================
* ======================================= sub.GetHomePos: $complex.pos = clone array: $a.sectorPos $complex.pos.size = size of array $complex.pos if $complex.pos.size == 3 append $complex.sector to array $complex.pos else if $complex.pos.size > 3 $complex.pos[3] = $complex.sector else $complex.pos = $complex.sector end endsub
* ======================================= sub.MoveHome: if [SECTOR] != $complex.sector gosub sub.GetHomePos [THIS] ->set destination to $complex.sector $sector = $complex.sector gosub sub.Resupply while [SECTOR] != $sector [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$remaining.text @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$complex.pos if $ret == FLRET_NOPATH $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=2123, null, null, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$text @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.idle.timeout : timeout in sec=120 wait while docked=[TRUE] end @ = wait 1000 ms end [THIS] ->set destination to null end endsub
* ======================================= sub.CheckOOS: if $DEFINE.OOSMOVE while [THIS] -> is in active sector $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=318, null, null, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$text @ = wait 500 ms @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.idle.timeout : timeout in sec=120 wait while docked=[TRUE] @ = wait 500 ms end $text = read text: page=$page.id id=283 [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$text end endsub
* ======================================= sub.SearchTubes: $ret.continue = null gosub sub.NeededTubes gosub sub.BuyTubes gosub sub.NeededTubes if $tubes > 0 if $v if not [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $v in cargo bay $got.tubes = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $v in cargo bay if $got.tubes > 0 $negate = - $got.tubes $got.tubes = [THIS] -> add $negate units of $v do if $got.tubes < 0 $got.tubes = - $got.tubes $stored.extensions = $stored.extensions + $got.tubes gosub sub.StoreData end end if [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $v in cargo bay $shipyard = $array.kits[3] if $shipyard if [DOCKEDAT] != $shipyard $sector = $shipyard -> get sector gosub sub.Resupply [THIS] ->set destination to $shipyard @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$shipyard if $sector == [SECTOR] @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetostation : station=$shipyard end end
[THIS] ->set destination to null @ = wait 1000 ms
if [DOCKEDAT] == $shipyard @ = wait 3000 ms gosub sub.BuyTubes end $ret.continue = [TRUE] endsub end end end end endsub
* ======================================= sub.StoreData: $store.data = array alloc: size=14 $store.data[0] = $a.sectorPos $store.data[1] = $a.complex $store.data[2] = $table.stations $store.data[3] = $table.shipyards $store.data[4] = $stations.array $store.data[5] = $position.array $store.data[6] = $mines.not.moved $store.data[7] = $table.built $store.data[8] = $total.stations $store.data[9] = $complex.hub $store.data[10] = $complex.tubes $store.data[11] = $table.existing $store.data[12] = $table.remove $store.data[13] = $stored.extensions [THIS] ->set local variable: name='build.complex' value=$store.data endsub
* ======================================= sub.MoveToBuildStation: gosub sub.MoveHome $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=289, null, null, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$text $x = $a.sectorPos[0] $y = $a.sectorPos[1] $z = $a.sectorPos[2] @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetoposition : sector=$complex.sector position x=$x position y=$y position z=$z precision=35000 endsub
* ======================================= sub.BuiltStation: while [SECTOR] != $complex.sector gosub sub.MoveToBuildStation @ = wait randomly from 10000 to 20000 ms end
$idx = get index of $station.type in array $stations.array offset=-1 + 1 if $idx > -1 $positions = $position.array[$idx] $table = $a.complex['asteroids'] @ $station = [THIS] -> call script !lib.build.station : Station Type=$station.type Build Position=$positions Not in Position table=$mines.not.moved Asterods Table=$table Owner=$a.owner Sector=[SECTOR] if $station -> exists = [THIS] -> add -1 units of $station.type $table.built[$station] = [TRUE] remove element from array $stations.array at index $idx remove element from array $position.array at index $idx gosub sub.StoreData end end endsub
* ======================================= sub.Buy: skip if $amt $amt = 1 $dock.owner = [DOCKEDAT] -> get owner race if $dock.owner == [TRUEOWNER] $amt = [THIS] ->load $amt units of $v, ignore minimum=[FALSE] else $amt = [THIS] -> buy $amt units of $v end if $amt if $table.bought[$v] $bought = $table.bought[$v] $bought = $bought + $amt $table.bought[$v] = $bought else $table.bought[$v] = $amt end end endsub
* ======================================= sub.MoveExistingStation: $ret.nopath = [FALSE] if not $station -> exists $station.type = $table.existing[$station] if $station.type == $complex.hub $idx = get index of $station.type in array $stations.array offset=-1 + 1 if $idx > -1 @ $array.kits = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getkits : Include HQ=$a.includeHQ Closest=[THIS] if $array.kits $stations.array[$idx] = $array.kits[0] end end end remove key $station from table $table.existing else $station.type = $station -> get ware type code of object $idx = get index of $station.type in array $stations.array offset=-1 + 1 if $idx > -1 while not [THIS] -> is in same sector as $station $sector = $station -> get sector @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$station if $ret == FLRET_NOPATH gosub sub.Idle $ret.nopath = [TRUE] endsub end @ = wait 1000 ms end @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetoobject.samesector : Target=$station Range=10000
gosub sub.CheckOOS
$table.built[$station] = [TRUE] $x = $position.array[$idx][0] $y = $position.array[$idx][1] $z = $position.array[$idx][2]
@ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetoposition : sector=$sector position x=$x position y=$y position z=$z precision=10000 @ = wait randomly from 2000 to 5000 ms
gosub sub.CheckOOS
$station ->set position: x=$x y=$y z=$z do if $station -> is of class Complex Hub $station ->set rotation: alpha=-16384 beta=0 gamma=0 remove element from array $stations.array at index $idx remove element from array $position.array at index $idx
do if $station.type == $complex.hub $complex.hub = $station
inc $stored.extensions = gosub sub.StoreData @ = wait randomly from 2000 to 5000 ms remove key $station from table $table.existing else if $station -> is of class Complex Hub $table.remove[$station] = [TRUE] remove key $station from table $table.existing end end endsub
* ======================================= sub.MoveExisting: if $table.existing $key = get next key: table=$table.existing key=null while $key @ = wait 500 ms $obj = $key $key = get next key: table=$table.existing key=$key
if not $obj -> exists remove key $key from table $table.existing continue end
if not $table.built[$obj] $sector = $obj -> get sector if $sector == $complex.sector gosub sub.MoveHome else @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$obj if $ret == FLRET_NOPATH gosub sub.Idle @ = wait 500 ms endsub end end
@ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetoobject.samesector : Target=$obj Range=10000
gosub sub.CheckOOS
if $obj -> is of class Complex Hub $aFacs = $obj ->get factories connected to complex if $aFacs $i = size of array $aFacs while $i dec $i = $station = $aFacs[$i] gosub sub.MoveExistingStation do if $ret.nopath endsub end end end $station = $obj gosub sub.MoveExistingStation do if $ret.nopath endsub end end end endsub
* ======================================= * Buy any stations from the docked shipiyard sub.BuyStations: $table.bought = table alloc
* get the stationos needed in a table with their total counts $table.tobuy = table alloc $i = size of array $stations.array while $i dec $i = $v = $stations.array[$i] if not is station type a complex construction kit: stationtype=$v if $table.tobuy[$v] $amt = $table.tobuy[$v] inc $amt = $table.tobuy[$v] = $amt else $table.tobuy[$v] = 1 end end end
* first try the station we originally came for $v = $station.type $amt = $table.tobuy[$v] gosub sub.Buy if $amt > 0 $check.amt = $table.tobuy[$v] $check.amt = $check.amt - $amt if $check.amt > 0 $table.tobuy[$v] = $check.amt else remove key $v from table $table.tobuy end end
* now try to buy any more $v = get next key: table=$table.tobuy key=null while $v $amt = $table.tobuy[$v] gosub sub.Buy $v = get next key: table=$table.tobuy key=$v end
* if we are buying the complex hub, also get the tubes to go with it if is station type a complex construction kit: stationtype=$station.type $complex.hub = $station.type gosub sub.StoreData gosub sub.BuyTubes end endsub
* ======================================= * Compute the number of tubes we need to get sub.NeededTubes: if $complex.hub -> exists $complex.type = $complex.hub -> get ware type code of object $complex.type = get construction kit from complex type: $complex.type $tubes = get complex connection tubes count: stationtype=$complex.type else $tubes = get complex connection tubes count: stationtype=$complex.hub end $tubes = $total.stations - $tubes - 1 if $tubes > 0 @ $array.kits = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getkits : Include HQ=$a.includeHQ Closest=[THIS] $v = $array.kits[2] if $v $got.tubes = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $v in cargo bay do if $got.tubes $tubes = $tubes - $got.tubes end do if $stored.extensions > 0 $tubes = $tubes - $stored.extensions end endsub
* ======================================= sub.BuyTubes: if [DOCKEDAT] gosub sub.NeededTubes if $tubes > 0 @ $array.kits = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getkits : Include HQ=$a.includeHQ Closest=[THIS] $v = $array.kits[2] if $v if [THIS] -> can buy ware $v at station [DOCKEDAT]
if not [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $v in cargo bay $got.tubes = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $v in cargo bay if $got.tubes $negate = - $got.tubes $got.tubes = [THIS] -> add $negate units of $v do if $got.tubes < 0 $got.tubes = - $got.tubes $stored.extensions = $stored.extensions + $got.tubes gosub sub.StoreData end end if [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $v in cargo bay $amt = [THIS] -> buy $tubes units of $v if $amt $complex.tubes = $v gosub sub.StoreData else $money = get player money $price = [DOCKEDAT] -> get price of ware $v if $price > $money $can.buy.race = [TRUE] $can.buy = [FALSE] gosub sub.Idle end end end end end end end endsub
* ======================================= sub.Idle: [THIS] ->set destination to null if not $can.buy.race $text = read text: page=$page.id id=286 else if not $can.buy $text = read text: page=$page.id id=285 else if not $can.buy.space $text = read text: page=$page.id id=287 else $text = read text: page=$page.id id=288 end [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$text
if not [DOCKEDAT] if [SECTOR] != $complex.sector $sector = $complex.sector gosub sub.Resupply gosub sub.GetHomePos @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$complex.pos end end
$rnd = random value from 15 to 30 - 1 @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.idle.timeout : timeout in sec=$rnd wait while docked=[TRUE] endsub
* ======================================= sub.Resupply: if [THIS] -> is autojump activated if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Navigation Command Software MK1 in cargo bay $resupply = [THIS] -> get jumpdrive fuel resupply do if $resupply $resupply = [THIS] ->get needed jump energy: jumps=$resupply $energy = [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay if $resupply > $energy $jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $sector $energy.needed = [THIS] ->get needed jump energy: jumps=$jumps if $energy.needed > $energy $energy.needed = $resupply - $energy $energy.free = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay if $energy.free >= $energy.needed dec $jumps = if $jumps >= 1 @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.resupply.self : Ware to Resupply=Energy Cells Quantity=$energy.needed Max Fly Range=$jumps end end end end end end end endsub
* ======================================= sub.GetStation: $can.buy.race = [FALSE] $can.buy = [FALSE] $can.buy.space = [FALSE] $station.type = null
$money = get player money
$use.hq = null if $a.includeHQ $hq = get player HQ if $hq -> exists $hq.sector = $hq -> get sector $hq.jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $hq.sector $can.jump = [FALSE] if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Navigation Command Software MK1 in cargo bay if [THIS] -> is autojump activated $can.jump = [TRUE] end end end
if $hq.jumps <= 5 OR $can.jump @ if [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$hq Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[FALSE] Additional Blacklist=null Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=null $use.hq = $hq end end @ = wait 100 ms end end
$i = size of array $stations.array while $i dec $i = $v = $stations.array[$i]
* save the complex hub until last $remaining = size of array $stations.array if $remaining > 1 do if is station type a complex construction kit: stationtype=$v continue end
* Get the best shipyard to buy from $shipyard = null if $use.hq -> exists do if $use.hq -> get amount of ware $v in cargo bay $shipyard = $use.hq end
if not $shipyard $shipyard = $table.shipyards[$v] if not $shipyard -> exists if [TRUEOWNER] == Player @ $shipyard = [THIS] -> call script lib.player.bestshipyard.station : Station Type=$v Closest Object=[THIS] Only Known=[TRUE] else @ $shipyard = [THIS] -> call script !lib.get.race.station : Race=[TRUEOWNER] Type=$v Closest To=[THIS] Only Known=[FALSE] Class/Type=Shipyard end end end
if $shipyard -> exists * check the sector blacklst, if we have already failed to get there $table.shipyards[$v] = $shipyard $sector = $shipyard -> get sector if $table.blacklist[$sector] $playing.time = playing time $time = $table.blacklist[$sector] if $time >= $playing.time remove key $sector from table $table.blacklist else continue end end
* check we can actually buy the station * have the notoriety, money and cargo space $sy.owner = $shipyard -> get owner race if $sy.owner == [TRUEOWNER] if $shipyard -> get amount of ware $v in cargo bay $can.buy = [TRUE] if [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $v in cargo bay $station.type = $v break end end else if [THIS] -> can buy ware $v from race $sy.owner if [THIS] -> can buy ware $v at station $shipyard $can.buy.race = [TRUE]
$price = $shipyard -> get price of ware $v if $money >= $price $can.buy = [TRUE] if [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $v in cargo bay $station.type = $v break end end end else * If we cant get the hub, try a different if is station type a complex construction kit: stationtype=$v @ $array.kits = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getkits : Include HQ=$a.includeHQ Closest=[THIS] $v = $array.kits[0] @ = wait 1000 ms $stations.array[0] = $v end * If we cant buy from race, then search for a shipyard where we can if [TRUEOWNER] == Player @ $shipyard = [THIS] -> call script lib.player.bestshipyard.station : Station Type=$v Closest Object=[THIS] Only Known=[TRUE] else @ $shipyard = [THIS] -> call script !lib.get.race.station : Race=[TRUEOWNER] Type=$v Closest To=[THIS] Only Known=[FALSE] Class/Type=Shipyard end do if $shipyard -> exists $table.shipyards[$v] = $shipyard @ = wait 1000 ms end end end end endsub
sub.AddStation: if $table.stations[$station.type] $amt = $table.stations[$station.type] inc $amt = $table.stations[$station.type] = $amt else $table.stations[$station.type] = 1 end endsub return null

comment.var: Build a Complex
Automatically builds a complx from a list of stations
Uses HephCorp do get the placement positions
The script will send the ship to the shipyard to buy each station
Author: Cycrow
set up the command texts, so the player knows whats going on

line.text: set command extra display override: text=

comment.var: if we are to restrore a previous attempt, check the stored data
not stored data to restore, so we start the process from the beginning
combine stations and mine tables

line.text: get ware type code of object
get ware type code of object
get ware type code of object

comment.var: get positions of station
find shipyards for all stationos
setup data storage
